{{Infobox building | name = Palace II | native_name = | image = | caption = | former_names = | building_type = [[Apartment building|Residential]] | architectural_style = | structural_system = | location = {{flagicon|Brazil}} [[Rio de Janeiro]], [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|RJ]], [[Brazil]]. | owner = | current_tenants = | landlord = | coordinates = | start_date = 1990 | completion_date = 1995 | demolition_date = February 28, 1998 | height = | diameter = | other_dimensions = | floor_count = 22 | floor_area = | main_contractor = | architect = | structural_engineer = | services_engineer = | civil_engineer = [[Sérgio Naya]] | other_designers = | quantity_surveyor = | awards = }} '''Palace II''' was a [[tower block]] built at [[Barra da Tijuca]], [[Rio de Janeiro (city)|Rio de Janeiro]], [[Brazil]]. On February 22, 1998, parts of it collapsed, due to engineering error, killing eight people.<ref>{{cite web |language=en, pt |url=http://www.unb.br/ics/dan/Serie274empdf.pdf |title=Das “Bravatas” – Mentira ritual e retórica da desculpa na cassaÇÃo de Sérgio Naya |trans-title=Das “Bravatas” - On boasting, ritual lies and the rhetoric of excuses |publisher=Universidade de Brasília/NuAP |author=Carla Costa Teixeira |format=PDF |location=Brasília |year=2000 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040416045023/http://www.unb.br/ics/dan/Serie274empdf.pdf |archive-date=2004-04-16 |access-date=2018-06-15 |dead-url=yes}}</ref> Another part of its structure collapsed on February 27, 1998 and the remaining parts of the building were demolished on February 28, 1998.<ref>{{cite news |language=pt |url=http://www.cpovo.net/jornal/A103/N151/HTML/default.htm |title=Mais um desabamento no prédio |trans-title=Another collapse of the building |publisher=Correio do Povo |website=www.correiodopovo.com.br |date=28 February 1998 |access-date=2018-06-15 |dead-url=no}}</ref> Before the building was demolished, researchers found empty [[Pier (architecture)|piers]] and evidence of the usage of [[beach]] [[sand]] on the construction.<ref>{{cite new |language=pt |url=http://www1.folha.uol.com.br/folha/cotidiano/ult95u374662.shtml |title=Desabamento do Palace 2 completa dez anos; vítimas buscam indenização |trans-title=10 years since the collapse of Palace 2; victims still seek compensation |publisher=Folha de Sao Paulo |author=Luisa Belchior |date=22 February 2008 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309173627/http://www1.folha.uol.com.br/cotidiano/2008/02/374662-desabamento-do-palace-2-completa-dez-anos-vitimas-buscam-indenizacao.shtml |archive-date=2016-03-06 |access-date=2018-06-15 |dead-url=yes}}</ref> All families had to move to hotels after the building’s fall. They had no time to collect their personal objects in their apartments.
Although most of them have not yet received any kind of [[indemnity]] from the company responsible for building their homes, the [[Superior Court of Justice (Brazil)|Superior Court of Justice of Brazil]] announced, on April 9, 2008, the unblocking of 13 million [[Brazilian real|reais]] (~6.5 million US dollars) earned through the [[auction]] of a property of [[Sérgio Naya]], the [[civil engineer]] who had designed and built the building,<ref>{{cite web |language=pt |url=http://www.endividado.com.br/materias_det.php?id=20497 |title=Palace II: STJ libera dinheiro de indenização a vítimas do desabamento |trans-title=Palace II: STJ releases relief money to victims of collapse |publisher=Endividado |author=Maria Fernanda Erdelyi |date=9 April 2008 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080504000553/http://www.endividado.com.br/materias_det.php?id=20497 |archive-date=2008-05-04 |access-date=2018-06-15 |dead-url=yes}}</ref> which will be given to the 130 families who lived there.
Sérgio Naya died on February 20, 2009, in [[Ilhéus]], due to a [[Myocardial infarction|heart attack]].<ref>{{cite news |language=pt |url=http://oglobo.globo.com/rio/mat/2009/02/20/morre-sergio-naya-dono-da-construtora-do-palace-2-754518605.asp |title=Morre Sérgio Naya, dono da construtora do Palace 2 |trans-title=Death of Sérgio Naya, owner of the company that build Palace 2 |publisher=[[O Globo]] |author=Ruben Berta |website=oglobo.globo.com |date=20 February 2009 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090223090026/https://oglobo.globo.com/rio/mat/2009/02/20/morre-sergio-naya-dono-da-construtora-do-palace-2-754518605.asp |archive-date=2009-02-23 |access-date=2018-06-15 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>
